## Monetization

### Free Tier

- 50 items total
- 3 collections
- All system types except `file` and `image`
- Basic search
- No file/image uploads
- No AI features

### Pro вҖ” $8/month or $72/year

- Unlimited items
- Unlimited collections
- File & image uploads
- Custom types *(coming later)*
- All AI features
- Export data (JSON / ZIP)
- Priority support

> **Implementation note:** The Pro gate should be set up from the start using the `isPro` flag on the User model, but all features remain unlocked during development.

