## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js 16 / React 19 |
| Language | TypeScript |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 + ShadCN UI |
| Database | Neon (PostgreSQL) |
| ORM | Prisma 7 |
| Auth | NextAuth v5 (Email + GitHub OAuth) |
| File Storage | Cloudflare R2 |
| AI | OpenAI `gpt-4o-mini` |
| Caching | Redis *(optional)* |
| Payments | Stripe |

> **Migration rule:** Never use `db push` to update the database schema. Always create and run explicit Prisma migrations in both dev and production.

