### Key Data Flow

```
User Action (e.g. "Save Snippet")
  вҶ’ React UI (drawer/form)
    вҶ’ POST /api/items
      вҶ’ Prisma вҶ’ Neon DB (save item)
      вҶ’ [if file] вҶ’ Cloudflare R2 (upload)
      вҶ’ [if Pro] вҶ’ OpenAI (auto-tag suggestion)
        вҶ’ Return item + tags to UI
          вҶ’ Toast notification
```

